Package: hrbrthemeslite
Type: Package
Title: Additional Themes, Theme Components and Utilities for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-02-27
Authors@R: c(
      person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rud.is", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Google", comment = "Roboto Condensed Font", role = c("cph"))
    )
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rud.is>
Description: A compilation of extra 'ggplot2' themes, scales and utilities with an overall
    emphasis on typography. A copy of the 'Google' font 'Roboto Condensed' 
    <https://github.com/google/roboto/> is also included to support one of the 
    typography-oriented themes.
URL: http://github.com/hrbrmstr/hrbrthemeslite
BugReports: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/hrbrthemeslite/issues
Copyright: file inst/COPYRIGHTS
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests:
    testthat,
    dplyr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    gridExtra,
    gcookbook
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1),
    grid,
    scales,
    extrafont,
    stringi,
    purrr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
